enseignements.objectif:
The main objective of this course is to offer a comprehensive understanding of the functioning of contemporary organizations and of the fundamentals of management. The students should develop competences in three areas:
' Content-specific: Knowledge of the fundamental management concepts, theories, and tools;
' Methodological: Application of established management tools; development of a business plan;
' Social: Collaborative work in teams on management issues; presentation skills.

